summary: MULTIPLE COILPACK PROBLEMS. 3 OUT OF 4 FAILED IN LESS THAN ONE YEAR OF OWNERSHIP. ONE COILPACK FELL APART IN MY HAND AS I REPLACED IT WITH AN AFTERMARKET PART. I PURCHASED AFTERMARKET REPLACEMENTS BECAUSE DEALER WAS UNABLE TO GET THE PART DUE TO OVERWHELMING FAILURES. THEY HAD 25 CARS ON THE LOT THAT WERE UNDRIVEABLE.
